00:15:18,250 --> 00:15:21,587
Bicara padanya setelah menurunkanku!

252
00:15:24,256 --> 00:15:25,507
Aduh.

253
00:15:27,092 --> 00:15:28,177
Kabur dari belakang.

254
00:15:29,553 --> 00:15:31,972
Si kecil ini bilang dia pemburu naga!

255
00:15:34,099 --> 00:15:36,477
Orang seperti kaulah

256
00:15:36,602 --> 00:15:38,145
yang merusak reputasi pemburu!

257
00:15:46,779 --> 00:15:48,614
Aduh.

258
00:15:48,697 --> 00:15:49,823
Maaf soal itu.

259
00:15:50,199 --> 00:15:51,992
Aku ceroboh dengan kakiku.

260
00:15:52,076 --> 00:15:52,910
Niko!

261
00:15:53,285 --> 00:15:57,331
Tolong jangan ganggu adik kami.

262
00:15:58,457 --> 00:16:00,417
Kalian menantang berkelahi, ya?

263
00:16:00,501 --> 00:16:02,753
Ada apa di sini? Tenanglah.

264
00:16:03,545 --> 00:16:05,631
Tolong lanjutkan di luar!

265
00:16:05,714 --> 00:16:06,840
Ini perkelahian!

266
00:16:10,636 --> 00:16:13,430
Maaf, tinjuku ceroboh.

267
00:16:15,683 --> 00:16:17,059
Baik, ayo bermain.

268
00:16:24,733 --> 00:16:26,193
Mereka sedang apa?

269
00:16:26,276 --> 00:16:27,778
Kau tak membantu mereka?

270
00:16:27,861 --> 00:16:30,614
Tidak, terima kasih. Aku pencinta damai.

271
00:16:31,782 --> 00:16:32,825
Tolong berhenti...

272
00:16:33,158 --> 00:16:34,618
Ini gila.

273
00:16:36,286 --> 00:16:37,413
Barku!

274
00:16:38,622 --> 00:16:39,623
- Ikut aku!
- Hei!

275
00:16:40,207 --> 00:16:41,041
Hei!

276
00:16:49,008 --> 00:16:50,884
Gadis ini menakjubkan!

277
00:16:52,761 --> 00:16:54,096
Aku menyerah.

278
00:16:54,722 --> 00:16:56,306
Hidup Vannie kami!

279
00:16:56,390 --> 00:16:58,475
Kau bahkan tak terlihat mabuk!

280
00:17:04,481 --> 00:17:06,316
Kios makanan sudah didirikan.

281
00:17:07,317 --> 00:17:10,487
Akan ada festival tahunan lusa.

282
00:17:11,613 --> 00:17:13,699
- Siapa namamu?
- Giraud.

283
00:17:14,241 --> 00:17:15,492
Aku Katja.

284
00:17:15,909 --> 00:17:16,869
Terima kasih tadi.

285
00:17:17,411 --> 00:17:19,538
Berlari membuatku lapar.

286
00:17:22,499 --> 00:17:24,710
LAGHMAN NAGA

287
00:17:24,793 --> 00:17:28,130
Aku suka menambahkan kacang
yang dihancurkan.

288
00:17:28,589 --> 00:17:30,382
Kami boleh makan di sana, Pak?

289
00:17:30,466 --> 00:17:32,885
- Tentu, tapi kembalikan mangkuknya.
- Ya!

290
00:17:37,973 --> 00:17:39,558
Wah, ini enak sekali!

291
00:17:40,809 --> 00:17:42,770
Lebih enak dengan kacang.

292
00:17:42,978 --> 00:17:45,397
Benar, 'kan? Makanlah!

293
00:17:47,232 --> 00:17:48,817
Meskipun kau yang bayar.

294
00:17:49,568 --> 00:17:50,694
Benarkah?

295
00:17:51,069 --> 00:17:54,823
Jadi, kau berkeliling dunia memburu naga.

296
00:17:56,742 --> 00:17:59,453
Mungkin daging ini dari naga
yang kau tangkap.

297
00:18:05,167 --> 00:18:07,961
Ceritakan kisah dari langit!

298
00:18:12,174 --> 00:18:14,218
Ayahku juga pemburu naga.

299
00:18:14,593 --> 00:18:17,513
Dia menceritakan banyak kisah
saat aku masih kecil.

300
00:18:18,555 --> 00:18:22,476
Di kapal kami,
ada pria luar biasa bernama Mika.

301
00:18:22,976 --> 00:18:26,772
Namun dia selalu masuk ke situasi gila
tanpa aku.

302
00:18:28,482 --> 00:18:29,817
Apa?

303
00:18:31,360 --> 00:18:32,194
Tunggu.

304
00:18:35,280 --> 00:18:36,865
- Ini.
- Terima kasih!

305
00:18:37,741 --> 00:18:41,370
Pasti menyenangkan bangun di atas awan
di pagi hari.

306
00:18:41,829 --> 00:18:44,206
Tak mudah hidup di langit.

307
00:18:45,457 --> 00:18:46,333
Kau tahu,

308
00:18:47,042 --> 00:18:49,169
aku tak pernah keluar dari kota ini.

309
00:18:50,087 --> 00:18:52,589
Aku di sini sejak kecil, saat aku dijual.

310
00:18:53,966 --> 00:18:55,050
Aneh, 'kan?

311
00:18:55,592 --> 00:18:59,304
Aku tinggal di kota pelabuhan,
tapi belum pernah ke mana-mana.

312
00:19:06,812 --> 00:19:08,230
Aku harus kembali.

313
00:19:08,897 --> 00:19:10,774
Terima kasih mau mengobrol denganku.

314
00:19:10,858 --> 00:19:14,736
Aku hanya bisa melihat festival
dari jendelaku.

315
00:19:15,529 --> 00:19:18,073
Aku senang bisa mengalaminya.

316
00:19:19,867 --> 00:19:20,909
Dah.

317
00:19:22,828 --> 00:19:23,829
Hei!

318
00:19:24,538 --> 00:19:25,747
Kita harus...

319
00:19:26,665 --> 00:19:28,000
kemari lagi lusa!

320
00:19:38,260 --> 00:19:39,303
Dah.

321
00:19:48,270 --> 00:19:51,732
Aku muak dengan kalian.

322
00:19:51,815 --> 00:19:54,109
Apa yang kalian pikirkan?

323
00:19:54,192 --> 00:19:56,737
Kalian harus memikirkan perbuatan kalian.

324
00:19:56,820 --> 00:19:57,905
Soraya!

325
00:19:57,988 --> 00:20:00,866
Kau juga bersalah hanya menonton
dan tak menghentikan mereka!

326
00:20:00,949 --> 00:20:02,868
Apa? Itu tak adil!

327
00:20:02,951 --> 00:20:04,995
Dari mana kau, Giraud?

328
00:20:05,662 --> 00:20:07,706
Kau yang mulai semua ini!

329
00:20:10,334 --> 00:20:12,211
Kenapa dia?

330
00:20:13,128 --> 00:20:15,714
Kenapa kalian babak belur?

331
00:20:15,797 --> 00:20:18,008
Ini tanda pria sejati.

332
00:20:18,800 --> 00:20:19,968
Tampak menyakitkan.

333
00:20:25,557 --> 00:20:26,558
Boleh duduk?

334
00:20:28,143 --> 00:20:29,061
Vannie.

335
00:20:30,187 --> 00:20:31,772
Kau minum-minum lagi?

336
00:20:32,272 --> 00:20:33,190
Sedikit.

337
00:20:33,899 --> 00:20:35,609
Aku ingin menyadarkan diri.

338
00:20:37,653 --> 00:20:38,487
Vannie.

339
00:20:39,321 --> 00:20:40,280
Ya?

340
00:20:41,615 --> 00:20:42,741
Aku ingin tahu...

341
00:20:43,992 --> 00:20:44,910
Lupakan saja.

342
00:20:55,087 --> 00:20:55,921
Kapal kita!

343
00:21:13,271 --> 00:21:15,649
Bagaimana naga itu bisa bergerak?

344
00:22:59,586 --> 00:23:01,838
Terjemahan subtitle oleh Serina Rajagukguk

